videos.description: Michael Ojo takes the lob pass from Xavier Rathan-Mayes and finishes with the dunk.
videos.headline: Ojo slams it home

videos.description: Christ Koumadje runs the court and finishes alley oop with the slam as Florida State pulls within 21-15.
videos.headline: FSU's Koumadje finishes strong

videos.description: Justin Robinson hits the 3 from the wing as Virginia Tech takes a 24-19 lead.
videos.headline: VT's Robinson drains the 3-pointer

videos.description: Seth Allen hits the 3-pointer to give Virginia Tech a 33-29 lead.
videos.headline: VT's Allen hits from behind the arc

videos.description: Virginia Tech head coach Buzz Williams wants his team to play better in the paint.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech head coach Buzz Williams discusses 1st half.

videos.description: Ahmed Hill uses the ball fake and then drives to the hoop for the basket and draws the foul.
videos.headline: VT's Hill drives strong to the basket for the and-1 bucket

videos.description: Xavier Rathan-Mayes grabs the offensive rebound and hits the putback as the Seminoles take a 43-38 lead.
videos.headline: Florida State swarming the glass for bucket

videos.description: Jonathan Isaac drains the 3 from the wing to give FSU a 48-42 lead.
videos.headline: FSU's Isaac hits from long range

videos.description: Terance Mann drains the corner 3 to give FSU a 55-52 lead.
videos.headline: Mann's 3-pointer gives Seminoles 2nd-half lead

videos.description: Dwayne Bacon optimistic about Seminoles' chances after victory of Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Florida State's Dwayne Bacon discusses win over Virginia Tech
